originalText.text:
Los paquetes llegaron incompletos y no se hacen responsables. Si envias aqui pide tu recibo completo que detalle tus pagos...cuanto es el servicio y cuanto es el seguro y cuanto valor tienen tus paquetes. Y aun asi ellos te aseguraran que nunca les a pasado y nunca les pasara, solo por que ellos lo dicen. Y los contenidos que no llegaron son tu problema. Mis envios llegaron pero, las cajas alguien las habrio y volvieron a sellar. Entonces ellos no se hacen responsables.

Fraudulent business who will not be responsible for any altered packages. I lost very valuable items and never asked for any $$ all I wanted was my things that were of sentimental value back and to return the items that were not mine. For a small family owned business it is such a shame they are not only not responsible but they are rude and just brush people off. They claim to have never had any issues and simply tell you what you are saying is impossible. Therefore, it is their word against yours.   I am sure I am not the only person  its happened to but he thinks people will just take their loss and move on. If you do come here make sure you get an itemized receipt, record as your packages are sealed and when they are picked up at their destination until they are opened, but I would definitely not recommend this business to anyone. Take your hard earned $ elsewhere.
